      [
      {Dorothy met three friends on her adventure to the Emerald City. With a Scarecrow in search of a brain, a Tin Woodsman looking to regain his heart, and a Cowardly Lion wishing for courage, she finally found herself looking at the great Wizard herself.

‘I want to go back home. Please grant me my wish.’

 The one they had thought to be the great all-powerful Wizard instead gave them directions.}
