      [
      {‘You have those wonderful silver shoes, no? If you follow the yellow brick road with those, you'll eventually reach your home. But, you'll have to make haste, for it's quite a long journey. When you get there, make sure to say it was the Great Wizard who granted your wish.’

 And so, Dorothy said her goodbyes and started on her journey home. The road was extremely long, enveloped by darkness once out of the brilliant glamour of the Emerald City. After a long time, she spotted her house in the distance - but when she arrived, all she found was a sad pile of destroyed rubble.

 The silver-shoed girl headed back to the Emerald City.}
