      {The Emerald City still shone vibrantly, but the Great Wizard Oz was nowhere to be seen.  She had first sent the clever human girl away, then played tricks and decieved the rest of the girl's friends, who killed Oz in a rage.

‘Y-you wicked Wizard! My friends, you've stripped me of my friends!’

 Dorothy, unable to reach her home after days and months of walking, decided to call all her friends and return home together.

 Four friends, who had started on a journey with a feeble hope dependant on a a swindler. The only ones who they could trust and rely on were each other.사기꾼에게 실낱같은 희망을 품고 서로를 도와가며 여행을 떠난 네 명의 친구들. 상처받은 그들이 믿고 의지할 수 있는 건 서로밖에 없었다.}
